            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Shigally Hill International Academy is one of the best boarding school in Dehradun.Its scenic campus amongst greenery attracts girls around the vicinity to study in this school.The highly qualified and dedicated educators, school Principal,advisors, residential staff and diverse student body create a modern learning experience for the students in a safe and stimulating campus.One of the best things about Shigally is that the school takes a holistic approach towards learning. The school develops students academic and personal growth through hands on learning opportunities and intercultural experiences.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
