            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Shigally Hill International Academy has been an exceptional institution for my child's educational journey. The dedicated teachers, supportive staff, and inclusive environment have fostered a love for learning and growth. The curriculum is well-rounded, and the extracurricular activities have helped develop valuable skills. Communication with parents is regular and transparent. I highly recommend to anyone seeking a nurturing and challenging environment for their child.\"",
